{
  "stem": "1132.1",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "I remember my mother-- when my father was placed into a forced labor camp around '41, '42, I believe, and when he had to go-- it was a situation where he had to go every day, every morning, and then he was allowed to come back home-- that my mother was running the law practice-- obviously she was no lawyer-- with a very close non-Jewish friend of my father who was an attorney.",
      "word_count": 73
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So for a couple of years, we were managing and the law practice was surviving because this man had agreed to run the practice and give my mother the proceeds-- my parents the proceeds-- which was quite an unusual thing for a non-Jew to do.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I think there were a number of people who have elected to do that for their Jewish friends.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I have recollections and a couple of pictures, which I hope we will take a picture of later, of my father working at this labor camp inside Hungary, pretty close to Budapest, which was a slaughtering house.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He actually wor-- worked at a slaughtering house and was very much involved in what the work was there.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Now, things started getting bad by '43, '44.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The pressure on professionals was really mounting, the-- that they were not allowed to practice.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It is my understanding-- I have a document that attests to that-- that as-- there was a special law passed by the Hungarian government.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The head of the government, by the way, was a gentleman called Miklos Horthy, who was an admiral of a country that had no beach and no access to any sea.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But he declared himself an admiral.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And his pictures were showing him on a white horse.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "That was his very famous pictures.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
